OL,3,CHouseholds suffer miserable year of
OL,4,Cacross-the-board bill increases
OL,6,FThis year has been a miserable one for
OL,7,Fhouseholds after across-the-board
OL,8,Fprice hikes on everything from energy
OL,9,Fto council tax left many struggling to
OL,10,Fbalance their budgets.
OL,12,FThe so-called "Awful April" price
OL,13,Fhikes combined with high energy costs
OL,14,Fsaw the average household facing an
OL,15,Fannual increase of #1,254 from
OL,16,Fessential bill rises, according to
OL,17,Ffigures from comparison site Uswitch.
