OL,3,CHouseholds suffer miserable year of
OL,4,Cacross-the-board bill increases
OL,6,FMost areas in England saw council tax
OL,7,Fbills rise by 5% ` the maximum amount
OL,8,Fpermitted ` with some including
OL,9,FBirmingham, Bradford, Newham,
OL,10,FSomerset, Trafford, and Windsor &
OL,11,FMaidenhead granted special permission
OL,12,Fto go even higher.
OL,14,FWater bills increased by an average
OL,15,F#123 per year ` the largest rise since
OL,16,Fthe industry was privatised in 1989.
