OL,4,Cacross-the-board bill increases
OL,6,FBroadband and phone bills also rose
OL,7,Fwhile the cost of a TV licence and the
OL,8,Fstandard rate of car tax both
OL,9,Fincreased by #5 ` with electric
OL,10,Fvehicles no longer exempt.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Ofgem's energy price cap `
OL,13,Fwhich sets bills for households still
OL,14,Fon standard variable tariffs rather
OL,15,Fthan fixed deals sought out
OL,16,Findependently ` started the year at
OL,17,F#1,738 for the average household and
OL,18,Fwill end it at #1,755 before it rises
OL,19,Fto #1,758 on January 1.
