OL,3,CHouseholds suffer miserable year of
OL,4,Cacross-the-board bill increases
OL,6,FUswitch spokeswoman Sabrina Hoque
OL,7,Fsaid: "Pressure points have been
OL,8,Fwidespread. Energy debt hit an eight-
OL,9,Fyear high in October, with households
OL,10,Fnow owing #780 million to their
OL,11,Fsuppliers. The strain is so severe
OL,12,Fthat more than two million homes say
OL,13,Fthey won't turn on their heating this
OL,14,Fwinter ` a fifth higher than last year.
