OL,3,CHouseholds suffer miserable year of
OL,4,Cacross-the-board bill increases
OL,6,FCitizens Advice chief executive Dame
OL,7,FClare Moriarty said: "The cost-of-
OL,8,Fliving crisis is not over. Stubbornly
OL,9,Fhigh bills and increasing living costs
OL,10,Fmean four million people are in a
OL,11,Fnegative budget, meaning they can't
OL,12,Fafford essentials like energy bills,
OL,13,Frent, or food.
OL,15,F"Our advisers see the impact of these
OL,16,Fpunishingly high costs every day.
OL,17,FPeople come to us feeling like they're
OL,18,Fconstantly fighting to stay afloat
OL,19,Fbut, despite their best efforts, are
OL,20,Fsinking further into the red.
