OL,6,F"Everyone should be able to afford the
OL,7,Fessentials and that's why better
OL,8,Ftargeted support is crucial. We want
OL,9,Fthe Government to increase Local
OL,10,FHousing Allowance to help those
OL,11,Fstruggling with their rent and improve
OL,12,Fbill support to ensure sky-high
OL,13,Futility costs, like energy and water,
OL,14,Fdon't continue to stretch household
OL,15,Fbudgets beyond breaking point."
